🚀 AI SaaS Platform

A full-stack AI-powered SaaS application built using the PERN/MERN stack that provides multiple AI tools like content generation, image processing, and automation features with secure authentication and payment integration.

📌 Features
🔐 Authentication & Authorization
OAuth login (Google, GitHub, etc.)
Secure session handling using Clerk / JWT
💳 Payment Integration
Subscription-based model using Stripe / Razorpay
Plan-based feature access
🧠 AI Tools Included
✍️ Article Generator
📝 Blog Title Generator
🎨 AI Image Generator
🖼️ Background Remover
🧹 Object Remover
📊 Dashboard
User activity tracking
Credits usage system
Tool usage history
⚡ Performance & Scalability
REST API architecture
Optimized backend with Node.js & Express
PostgreSQL / MongoDB database support
🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend
React.js
Tailwind CSS / Bootstrap
Axios
Backend
Node.js
Express.js
Database
PostgreSQL / MongoDB
AI Integration
OpenAI API / Google GenAI API
Authentication
Clerk / JWT Auth
Payment
Stripe / Razorpay
📁 Project Structure

1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-saas-platform.git
cd ai-saas-platform
2. Install dependencies
# Backend
cd backend
npm install

# Frontend
cd ../frontend
npm install
3. Setup Environment Variables

Create a .env file in backend:

PORT=5000
DATABASE_URL=your_database_url
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key

# AI APIs
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_ai_key

# Auth
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=your_clerk_key

# Payment
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=your_stripe_key
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_key
RAZORPAY_SECRET=your_secret
4. Run the project
# Run backend
npm run dev

# Run frontend
npm start
🔗 API Endpoints (Sample)
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/auth/login	User login
POST	/api/ai/generate	Generate AI content
POST	/api/payment	Handle subscription
GET	/api/user/dashboard	User dashboard data
🧪 Testing
API testing using Postman
Unit testing (optional)
🚀 Deployment
Frontend: Vercel / Netlify
Backend: Render / Railway / AWS
Database: Supabase / MongoDB Atlas
